videos.headline: Illinois RB Foster breaks tackle, scores 31-yard TD
videos.description: Illinois RB Kendrick Foster eludes Nebraska's defense and rushes 31 yards for the touchdown to tie the game against Nebraska.

videos.headline: Newby blows by the defense to clinch Nebraska's win
videos.description: Nebraska running back Terrell Newby runs through the middle of the Illini defense to score a 62-yard touchdown to give the Cornhuskers a 31-16 lead.
